{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, future studies should involve participants from developed countries to improve the generalizability of the results.",
    "Second, the temporal factor must be acknowledged, as this study was conducted in 2023, and AI technologies will continue to evolve rapidly.",
    "Finally, the study's qualitative approach captured subjective perceptions.",
    "Future research should incorporate quantitative measures for a more comprehensive understanding of the effects of ChatGPT.",
    "Future research should explore various avenues to further enhance our understanding of the role of ChatGPT in academia."
  ]
}